question_text: Was there an adequate control? If so, highlight section.
target_text: split the group into patients who happened to be assigned to doctors who prescribed a lot of opioids, and patients who met doctors who didn’t. target_text: the patients who, by chance, saw a doctor who more frequently prescribed the drugs were 30 percent more likely to become long-term users of painkillers.
